lead_paragraph: Jared Goff lobbed a few balls to a couple of lucky kids and practiced his coverage skills. Carson Wentz grinned as he sent a line of boys and girls through a footwork drill.

headline.print_headline: Goff, Wentz at Ease on Eve of NFL Draft
